---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="CA Accounting | Glendale CPA & Tax Firm Serving California"
  description="An AICPA-member accounting firm in Glendale, CA. Led by a CPA and an Enrolled Agent. Specialists in entertainment, medical practice, and real estate accounting for over 20 years."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-cream-warm">
    <div class="container-custom py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">
          Glendale, California · Established Firm · Over 20 Years
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-serif font-semibold text-navy leading-[1.05] mb-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          A Glendale CPA firm built on twenty years of trust.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-10 fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          AICPA-member firm. Led by a Certified Public Accountant and an Enrolled Agent. Specialists in entertainment, medical practice, and real estate accounting for clients across California and beyond.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:8775009290"
            class="border border-navy text-navy font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-navy hover:text-cream transition-colors"
          >
            Call 877.500.9290
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we do -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">What We Do</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Three areas of practice.<br />One unified team.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Whether you need year-round tax planning, dependable bookkeeping, or strategic financial leadership, the work is handled by senior professionals who know your business.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-line rounded-lg p-8 fade-in">
          <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-forest mb-6"></div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Tax & Planning</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Year-round tax strategy, return preparation, IRS representation, and multi-state filings for individuals, businesses, and trusts.
          </p>
          <a href="/services#tax" class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm hover:text-forest-hover transition-colors">
            Tax services →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-line rounded-lg p-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-forest mb-6"></div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Accounting & Bookkeeping</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Outsourced bookkeeping, payroll, financial statement preparation, and reviews — built for owners who'd rather run the business than the back office.
          </p>
          <a href="/services#accounting" class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm hover:text-forest-hover transition-colors">
            Accounting services →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-line rounded-lg p-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-forest mb-6"></div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">CFO & Advisory</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Outsourced CFO support, cash flow management, business valuations, and M&A advisory. The financial leadership of a senior hire, scaled to what your company actually needs.
          </p>
          <a href="/services#cfo" class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm hover:text-forest-hover transition-colors">
            CFO services →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries we know -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Industries We Know</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
          Specialists, not generalists.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We've spent two decades building deep expertise in three industries that ask more of their accountants than most. If you work in one of these fields, you'll be working with people who already know your numbers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/industries/entertainment" class="group bg-navy-deep border border-cream/10 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-cream/30 transition-colors fade-in">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-4">Entertainment</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Working musicians, actors, producers, directors, and the agencies behind them. Tour accounting, royalty tracking, residuals, loan-out structures, and IP valuation.
          </p>
          <span class="text-cream/90 font-semibold text-sm">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/industries/medical" class="group bg-navy-deep border border-cream/10 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-cream/30 transition-colors fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-4">Medical Practices</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Doctors, dentists, chiropractors, and veterinarians. Practice management, equipment depreciation, multi-entity structures, and physician retirement planning.
          </p>
          <span class="text-cream/90 font-semibold text-sm">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/industries/real-estate" class="group bg-navy-deep border border-cream/10 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-cream/30 transition-colors fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-4">Real Estate</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Property managers, developers, investors, brokers, and agents. Depreciation strategies, 1031 exchanges, multi-property bookkeeping, and K-1 handling.
          </p>
          <span class="text-cream/90 font-semibold text-sm">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why firms hire us -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Why Clients Stay</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
            The credentials. The continuity. The people.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Firms in the entertainment, medical, and real estate industries have specialized financial needs — and high stakes if they're handled wrong. CA Accounting was built specifically for clients who can't afford to learn that lesson the hard way.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Our partners hold CPA and Enrolled Agent credentials. The firm is an AICPA member. We've been doing this for over twenty years, with most of our team in place for the long term — so the person who learned your business this year will still be the person handling it five years from now.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="bg-cream-warm border border-line rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-serif text-navy font-semibold mb-2">20+</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Years of practice</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream-warm border border-line rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-serif text-navy font-semibold mb-2">11</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Team members</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream-warm border border-line rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-serif text-navy font-semibold mb-2">CPA</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Managing Partner credential</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream-warm border border-line rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-serif text-navy font-semibold mb-2">EA</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Founding Partner credential</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured testimonial -->
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 text-center">In Our Clients' Words</p>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-navy leading-snug mb-8 text-center">
          "It's always a pleasure working with Rima, Narek and Farshid at CA Accounting. They're not only wonderful people but also exceptionally talented, precise, and driven in their work. I've worked with them across two different companies now and can confidently recommend them to anyone looking for reliable accounting and finance support."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold">J. Sider</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Google Review · 5 stars</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other testimonials -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in">
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "The accounting team is trustworthy and reliable. They make it easy to work with and are great partners for entrepreneurs like me."
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Melva Benoit</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">The Marian Dupree Group</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "Couldn't be happier with the service at CA Accounting. Farshid, Lucy and the whole team. Very attentive to details and most important — knowledgeable. I highly recommend them."
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Ernie Fregozo</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">Google Local Guide</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "Farshid and his team really put in the work for our multiple, multi-state returns."
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Jean-Marc Cloutier</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">Google Review</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
          Bring us your numbers.<br />We'll bring you the strategy.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          The first conversation is free. We'll review your current books, understand what you're trying to accomplish, and tell you whether we're the right firm for the job — even if the answer is no.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:8775009290"
            class="border border-cream/40 text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-cream/10 transition-colors"
          >
            Call 877.500.9290
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
